      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "Holiness occurs when power and goodness co-exist in perfect harmony.\nadapted from Mordecai Kaplan\nHow shall we sanctify God's name? By being holy ourselves. How do we accomplish this? Let our\nprayers bring us to sacred deed, to actions that promote justice, harmony and peace.",
          "language": "en"
        }
